            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>At Farm-To-Go, we are dedicated to providing a reliable and user-friendly marketplace for Farmers & Customers alike. Our mission is to empower farmers and consumers to create a sustainable agricultural ecosystem, fostering environmental conservation, economic growth, and food security. We strive to connect farmers & customers through a secure and transparent system.</p>

            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> We are committed to promoting environmentally friendly practices that conserve resources, reduce waste, and prioritize long-term ecological balance in agriculture.</li>
                <li><strong>Empowerment:</strong> We strive to uplift Filipino farmers of all scales by providing accessible tools and opportunities, fostering economic growth, and bridging the gap between rural communities and modern markets.</li>
                <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> We value transparency, trust, and accountability, ensuring fair trade practices and authentic relationships between farmers and consumers.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or need more information, feel free to reach out to us:</p>
